thread.title_full: Win a great navigational bundle with Ordnance Survey - Telegraph

author: The Telegraph
title: Win a great navigational bundle with Ordnance Survey
text: Have you ever been out walking in the wilderness – or decided to take a short cut cross country – and suddenly wished you had a map and compass to hand? Well, here's a chance to get your hands on some invaluable navigational kit, courtesy of Ordnance Survey, the real experts in the field. Ten lucky winners will receive a prize package containing: a navigational bundle (including a Silva Carry Dry Map Case in size large, and a Silva Starter 8 Compass); an OS Custom Made Map – either the OS Explorer (1:25,000) Map or OS Landranger (1:50,000) Map; and 12 months’ subscription to OS Maps, starting from the date the code is activated. A superb prize for any outdoor enthusiast, all you need do to put yourself in the frame is enter your details below by midnight on 30 September 2015. Please note that entrants have up to 30 November 2015 to activate the subscription code. Online Form - Win a great navigational bundle with Ordnance Survey
